RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 1M 70Y All Weather Track CR: 61. Maiden Claiming Purse 21000. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 118 lbs. Claiming Price $12,500.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: READY ON THE LINE set the pace in the two path, opened up and was cued from the five path turning into the lane, and held sway. HEART BOY stalked in the four path early, tipped out to the six path down the backstretch and moved up going into the far turn, was driven from said position into the stretch, and chased home the winner for place. DREAM OF BLESSINGS tracked along the inside, evened out from the the two path in the stretch, but dug in late to hold on to show honors. COLLISION chased in the four path, was ridden from the six path into the stretch, but flattened out and hung late. NAPA DUDE raced off the pace in the four path, angled out and was coaxed from the seven path turning into the lane, drifted out in upper stretch, and was no factor. BUDDHA BOY broke in a tangle, was behind in the three path early and never threatened. GO GO GREEN prompted the pace in the five path but dropped back around the far turn.
